<exercise id="fs-idp72164784">
<problem id="fs-idp20721104"><para id="fs-idp19566304">Air is warmed and humidified in the nasal passages. This helps to ________.</para>
<list id="fs-idm50578528" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha">
<item>ward off infection</item>
<item>decrease sensitivity during breathing</item>
<item>prevent damage to the lungs</item>
<item>all of the above</item>
</list>
</problem>
